<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Delicious Pancake Recipe</title>
    <!-- Link to external CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>

<h1 id="mainTitle">Delicious Pancakes</h1>

<h2 class="heading">About Pancakes</h2>
<p class="paragraph">
You will need flour, milk, eggs, sugar, baking powder, butter, and a pinch of salt to make pancakes.
</p>

<h3 class="heading">Preparing the Batter</h3>
<p class="paragraph">
Mix the dry ingredients first. Then add eggs and milk and stir until the batter becomes smooth with no lumps.
</p>

<h3 class="heading">Cooking the Pancakes</h3>
<p class="paragraph">
Heat a pan on medium heat and add a little butter. Pour some batter into the pan and cook until bubbles form, then flip to cook the other side.
</p>

<h4 class="heading">Serving</h4>
<p class="paragraph">
Serve the pancakes warm with syrup, honey, fruits, or butter. They taste best fresh and can be enjoyed with family or friends.
</p>

<h4 class="heading">Conclusion</h4>
<p class="paragraph">
This pancake recipe is simple, delicious, and perfect for anyone who wants a tasty breakfast. Enjoy making and sharing them!
</p>

</body>
</html>

